dml.team5.antlr

Interface PLSQLListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PLSQLBaseListener, SelectedElementListener, TableListener

    public interface PLSQLListener
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by PLSQLParser.
